snippet.title: Hulk (Xbox/PS2 Game) - 2003 Trailer [High Quality]
snippet.description:
High quality trailer of the game based on the movie Hulk, released in 2003 for GameCube, PlayStation 2, Xbox and PC.

Source: Official Xbox Magazine (OXM) bonus DVD.
